{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1257/comments/3639067.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:5403cce08b2a..9abd63a84e3a?path=gazebo%2Fgui%2FModelListWidget.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1257/_/diff#comment-3639067"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1257, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1257.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1257"}}, "title": "Display joint type, parent link's name and child link's name on world tree"}, "content": {"raw": "We should add a helper function to msgs.cc for this logic. I have actually implemented the reverse in a branch ( a1ee8f3 ):\n~~~\nmsgs::Joint::Type Convert(const std::string &_str);\n~~~\n\nI would propose moving this switch statement to a new function:\n~~~\nstd::string Convert(const msgs::Joint::Type _type);\n~~~\n\nI can help with this and writing a unit test if necessary.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>We should add a helper function to msgs.cc for this logic. I have actually implemented the reverse in a branch ( <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/commits/a1ee8f3\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">a1ee8f3</a> ):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">msgs</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">Joint</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">Type</span> <span class=\"nt\">Convert</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">const</span> <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nt\">_str</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>I would propose moving this switch statement to a new function:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span> <span class=\"nt\">Convert</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">const</span> <span class=\"nt\">msgs</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">Joint</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">Type</span> <span class=\"nt\">_type</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>I can help with this and writing a unit test if necessary.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-10-28T18:36:56.232739+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": 1433, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/gui/ModelListWidget.cc"}, "updated_on": "2014-10-28T18:36:56.239813+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 3639067}